        {
            "title": "壁球｜跟埃及世界排名14激鬥奪亞   陳善鈺雖敗猶榮",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/dfe4959d549eddf92f0b2cd7eb7c5fcd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041023273010213.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港壁球代表陳善鈺周四在巴基斯坦卡拉奇的WSF U23世界壁球錦標賽女單決賽，跟世界排名14的埃及19歲新星Fayrouz Aboelkheir拉鋸了28分鐘，港將以10:12、9:11、6:11下馬，但仍為香港在這個首屆賽事取得歷史性首面銀牌。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳善鈺獲得第一屆U２３世錦賽奪亞。直播截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f1baa05e270e2aeeba4cc34c015473f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-10_at_10_51_19_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳善鈺獲得第一屆U２３世錦賽奪亞。直播截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"女子組三甲球員。香港壁總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b140be61976afc3fea27d2ecc512e6d3/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-10_at_11_21_21_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女子組三甲球員。香港壁總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港壁總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b55b1daed5bc2f4cc45b873e3eae93df/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-10_at_11_20_12_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港壁總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳善鈺奪獎後跟隊友及教練團合照。 香港壁總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1dab2f05974cc496a577913ac2c8d209/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-10_at_11_20_08_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳善鈺奪獎後跟隊友及教練團合照。 香港壁總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>現就讀美國哥倫比亞大學的陳善鈺，從16強打起，先後擊敗南非、日本及大馬對手，來到決賽對Fayrouz Aboelkheir，雙方世界排名相距超過60位，但善鈺在首局跟對方戰至刁時才輸，次局也是只相距2分，但在第3局，對方越戰越勇，善鈺未能得到任何甜頭下，以0:3敗陣，最終取得亞軍。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
